				<td colspan="2"><span>iv found that I will drift in the opposite direction im looking. I f9 out a few times get a side view of me running. So say im looking south i will drift slightly north. when i notice im getting too close to a wall or something i spin my camera angle so that i am looking north and i will start to drift slowly south clearing me of running into the wall. this works with me hope it might help ya. </span></td>
