				<td colspan="2"><span>I am very new at PBAE's, only a few under my belt atm. First few times I ran, got the drift and agroed the bigger brother that almost kicked my a$. I turned all song animation off and the issue was resolved, no more drift. I've got a G-Force 5200 256MB card, 2.4Ghz processor and high speed internet which I'm pretty sure helps the problem. I think it helps if you minimize your process loads so your comp can concentrate on telling the server exactly where your running. Just a suggestion, hope it helps.
